  <main>
    <h2>Innovation as a Core Value</h2>
    <p>Nike’s success has always been driven by innovation. From <strong>air cushioning technology</strong> to <strong>Flyknit</strong> materials, Nike continually evolves its design and production methods.</p>

    <h3>Key Innovations</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>1979:</strong> Introduction of Nike Air technology.</li>
      <li><strong>1985:</strong> Launch of the Air Jordan line with Michael Jordan.</li>
      <li><strong>2012:</strong> Debut of Flyknit, a lightweight, sustainable shoe design.</li>
      <li><strong>Today:</strong> Use of recycled materials and digital customization tools like Nike By You.</li>
    </ul>

    <img src="jordan.png" alt="Air Jordan 1 Retro" width="250">
